snippet.title: PicoHot || SuperHot  is now on Pico-8!
snippet.description:
The SuperHot Team has a mission to bring superhot to every possible platform. They now present PicoHot, the most innovative pico-8 game you've played in years! "Coming soon to smartfridges!" - SuperHot tweeted.

I play through the entire game with an endless mode, and a few levels.

You can play it here on the Pico-8 website: https://www.lexaloffle.com/bbs/?pid=74385#p
